{
  "stem": "5388.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And yep, I go back to my stamps to show him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, that's not a day for stamp collecting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But you see, Oberfeldwebel [GERMAN] is above him, so he was a little bit-- couldn't quite say, you know-- and--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stop now?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so then he walked away after bawling me out and this and that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I still stayed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took-- kind of stood my ground, in a sense.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't know where to turn, so I went ahead and I went to the outhouse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was an outhouse for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went into one, and I closed myself in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was sitting there and sitting there, and somebody used to come and knock on the outhouse to get in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When-- but then somebody, they got suspicious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Before you know it, two, three German soldiers come in, and knock, knock.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I open the outhouse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, is master here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What are you doing here, and what is that?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I started the same spiel all over again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oberfeldwebel [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I have my stamps, and I came to see him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he's not here yet, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They bought it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in the place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then somebody told me, OK, go on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went up there, and they put me in a room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Put me in a room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were two soldiers sitting in the-- at a table.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And behind them, as you entered it on the left side was those furniture type of things like you had in Europe, where you put in hanging the clothes in the closet, but it's not the closet with inside the walls, you know.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
